name: BIRTH OF ZANDER
description: ZANDER is the longest running character i've designed. originally created back in 2015, ZANDER was birthed through the stars...in deep space...since then he's taken shape into many forms that compliment each of his personalities and his trickster ways.. finally minted as a NFT, Sat April 17th 10:50 AM PST. by LEEAUX / https://leeaux.com
